{"tid":1597580,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"世新大學連儂牆","createTime":"2019-09-27T04:16:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T10:45:07.000Z","uid":259296,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2ace95e335cf763c7a2bdc3089cbc701259ba55b","tid":1597580,"uid":259296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:16:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Vt7YRb5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVt7YRb5.jpg&h=9121bc85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2618592074851623&amp;id=100001025695706\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D2618592074851623%26id%3D100001025695706&d=6kTjEm0JFzAR16ySTE8tYrhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=604698ee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=2618592074851623&amp;id=100001025695706</a><br />\n<br />\n希望各位黎台北既時候都可以來貼Memo<br />\n各位可以既話可以幫我轉發分享<br />\n<br />\n在台北居留港人亦可以黎支持下<br />\n<br />\n鑑於早前有大陸學生撕毀性別所關於反送中既海報，我地亦會輪流去看守連儂牆是否正常運作<br />\n<br />\n以及校方希望我地能將連儂牆移除一事，作為在校港生表達強烈不滿"},{"pid":"3604a967a882c28767c4e52ca54c86cc1f1810f8","tid":1597580,"uid":259296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:19:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"730fcd18ae07140f938bad83819f75f31fcf6123","tid":1597580,"uid":259296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:20:16.000Z","msg":"推到你地肯睇為止"},{"pid":"9e1a9fc4a1c01a95e42eddce131838e2c75f0d61","tid":1597580,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:20:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5955b7ab2686e715907767234da9c8796d95e414","tid":1597580,"uid":259296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T04:23:12.000Z","msg":"繼續推"},{"pid":"e18ff84fcca1b1fe898b3658a6f6289f1d869588","tid":1597580,"uid":259296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"c